Collection of helper modules for Xula-200 FPGA development board written in Verilog-2001.

Includes OmniVision camera initialization utilities, SDRAM controller, and PC <-> FPGA communication module.


Files: 
------

camera/            - Modules for initializing OmniVision camera chips.   
  SCCBCtrl.v         - SCCB controller. Provides communication over SCCB with OV cameras.
  CameraSetup.v      - Top module for camera initialization.
  OV7670Init.v       - Initialization register set for OV7670 model.

ClkGen.v           - Helper modules for working with clock signals.

HostIo.v           - PC <-> FPGA communication through the JTAG port.

SdramCtrl.v        - Single port SDRAM controller.

Math.v             - Math helper functions for other modules.

Test.v             - Top test/example module.



